{"tid":1815383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣佈三毛小隊希望正式退出抗爭","createTime":"2020-01-07T12:52:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T06:46:16.000Z","uid":55973,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a4bcff3a8e08ecd3335a34df9e17f5ddf9fb0bcb","tid":1815383,"uid":55973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:52:31.000Z","msg":"以下係三毛小隊既部分成員名單<br />\n希望連仔可以幫佢地退出抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【長期置頂】連登三毛清單 (持續更新)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1652371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1652371</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Dk_KqQv2LJPc5JFqmts9nANVg9TIGBZ-biecHxnhIlo/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1Dk_KqQv2LJPc5JFqmts9nANVg9TIGBZ-biecHxnhIlo%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TRPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=62df837b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Dk_KqQv2LJPc5JFqmts9nANVg9TIGBZ-biecHxnhIlo/edit#gid=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三毛小隊依半年黎雖然不停有新血加入，人數眾多，列極都列唔哂<br />\n但係同時亦都失去左唔少人<br />\n<br />\n以下節錄部份已消失成員既遺言<br />\n<br />\n書面語達人(五毛) ：「你屈毛！」<br />\n<br />\n人格分裂最強勇武 ：「屌哂你地班垃圾連登仔」<br />\n<br />\n一路好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未入名單/剩低既成員我地會繼續一直關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c04a3bfd358ce675371536470eaaaa9bfee50e","tid":1815383,"uid":55973,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r9FBWME.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr9FBWME.jpg&h=9a412321&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d82b95c5651ea524be0f674a9ff86a60fd08e12","tid":1815383,"uid":55973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:57:35.000Z","msg":"希望連仔快D幫佢地退出抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3139aad7d26939dcb93a6b6ba6aa9387f13a916c","tid":1815383,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:58:44.000Z","msg":"咱们维稳部会坚守岗位，确保2047香港一国一制的实行"},{"pid":"c9b2deba8fbd0a3253fb0e717c8ca7a51ad9b01b","tid":1815383,"uid":55973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:02:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a37e3276ceab0dc616fa3083425139e8ac7f869","tid":1815383,"uid":91192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3139aad7d26939dcb93a6b6ba6aa9387f13a916c","tid":1815383,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:58:44.000Z","msg":"咱们维稳部会坚守岗位，确保2047香港一国一制的实行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:05:33.000Z","msg":"唔洗喇唔該<br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"390ea127e07f57c59e23de26d0b2eaeb90b2e05b","tid":1815383,"uid":55973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:10:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57977ce04dde8f331362ec9c8efe85a7ff121889","tid":1815383,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_combo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_combo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_combo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6c10ff79333549e7e4900d3ef55c7a9574eb15","tid":1815383,"uid":55973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57977ce04dde8f331362ec9c8efe85a7ff121889","tid":1815383,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_combo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets